reviews.review_text: Largely Lacking Thanx Russ.  I was at this show and have not heard it in 20 years.  The quality is as stated by taper.  I was happy to get this as I was there.  For everyone else a good listen before downloading is in order.  The Black Peter is the highlight for me.  Bertha, Playing, Terrapin to open the 2nd set was nice but like the rest of the show punchless.  I am playing Uncle>River on my radio show tomorrow.  Peace
